Age limit
Our services are available only for people aged 18 and over. We do not deliberately collect personal information from children under 18.
Disclose and share your information
1. We use third parties to help us operate and improve our services. These third parties assist us with a variety of tasks, including hosting and maintenance, continuous development, analytics, customer service, marketing, advertising. We may also share information with advertising partners who distribute ads in our services.
2. We will never provide or provide any information to a third party without your prior consent. If your personal information is required by law or disclosed in good faith, we may disclose your personal information if we consider such actions necessary to comply with legal obligations, and to protect and defend our rights or property.
